H0.text: In the computing acronym WYSIWYG (wiziwig) what word is represented by both letter Ws. What

H1.text: In the computing acronym WYSIWYG (wiziwig) what word is represented by both letter Ws. Will

H2.text: In the computing acronym WYSIWYG (wiziwig) what word is represented by both letter Ws. Wish

H3.text: In the computing acronym WYSIWYG (wiziwig) what word is represented by both letter Ws. Wut

A4.text: In computing, WYSIWYG ( WIZ-ee-wig; what you see is what you get) is software that allows content to be edited in a form that resembles its appearance when printed or displayed as a finished product, such as a printed document, web page, or slide presentation.
